snippet.title: Mecha BREAK - Gameplay Overview Trailer | gamescom 2024
snippet.description: Check out the lightning arial combat and cybernetic abilities in Seasun Games' upcoming multiplayer action game, Mecha BREAK, coming to PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S, and PC in 2025.
